  * debian/mozilla-firefox.install: Don't install
    /usr/lib/mozilla-firefox/extensions/reporter@mozilla.org, it got moved in
    the chrome.

 -- Mike Hommey <glandium@debian.org>  Tue,  1 Nov 2005 22:01:15 +0100

