    Apply ported patch from Serge Belyshev from bz#293307 to fix problem
    with gcc-4.0 on amd64. (Closes: #319336)
  * debian/rules: Remove silly --enable-freetype configure line. Thanks
    Antony Gelberg. (Closes: #319886)

