  * Apply patch to make forward and back buttons work on mice. (Closes:
    #211606)
  * debian/rules: Use -O optimization on alpha, so it will build
    again. (Closes: #213603)
  
 -- Eric Dorland <eric@debian.org>  Fri,  3 Oct 2003 00:07:44 -0400

